WRITING.TITLE: I can see why Spielberg didn't use this T-Rex
Tried to upgrade my cats wardrobe. He was having none of it

WRITING.TEXT: This one lady opened up to me and started crying. She said "did you ever reach that certain age where you realized you outgrew everything?"
I don't mean to brag about it. More so, we had a ton of fun and there's a dude in a bacon suit. I guess my poor choice of wording for a good time
